Full production changes:
1. Switch to postgres
2. logging
3. testing
4. Add ability to have simultaneous projects
5. Only admin can register new users for a project
6. Only admin can upload
7. If twitter API fails we should display the text we have in the db
8. re-write form validation in the index view
9. Enable Nested/contingent categories
10. Mark private functions
11. Deleting a code should unset the coded/recoded boolean in the tweet table
12. Deleting a project should cascade delete the tweets, codes, users and categories
13. Better handling for failed file uploads
14. Styling to CSS
15. On setting a project set a cron job to regularly gather tweets
16. Global & project admins (project admins can only see their own
    projects and users)
